d:
This is not a duplicate. https://e-hentai.org/g/3536109/cf71f1babb/ contains a bunch of sketches, and I'd like to maintain a version of the archive without the sketches.

I have obtained these files from The Jab Archives here: https://www.jabarchives.com/main/gallery/area/293

Once the entire comic has been released, I will be happy to let this one be expunged as a duplicate, but until then, I would like to maintain this version without the sketches.

Edit: I have realized that apparently the other version has higher resolution images, but also there are slight differences between this version and the other version. The most obvious difference being that page 2 of the archive (page 1 of the comic) shows an establishing shot of the dormitory in 3536109, but in this one, it's the school.
